We have digitised our Tatar edition of Mehmed Yazıcıoğlu’s Muhammediyye. Written in the Anatolian-Turkish vernacular of the 15th century, the text seemed understandable to a Tatar audience at around 1900.
Now in #openaccess: https://t.co/K4AHQjv6TF
